.Dd February 15, 2026
.Dt WHISPER-SERVER 1
.Os Mozilla.ai 
.Sh NAME
.Nm whisper-server
.Nd HTTP server for speech to text
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op flags...
.Fl m Ar model.gguf
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
provides an HTTP API for speech-to-text transcription using OpenAI's
Whisper model. It accepts audio file uploads and returns transcriptions
in various formats including JSON, plain text, SRT, and VTT.
.Pp
Supported audio formats are WAV, MP3, FLAC, and OGG.
.Sh OPTIONS
The following options are available:
.Bl -tag -width indent
.It Fl Fl version
Print version and exit.
.It Fl h , Fl Fl help
Show help message and exit.
.It Fl m Ar FNAME , Fl Fl model Ar FNAME
Path of Whisper model weights. See
https://huggingface.co/ggerganov/whisper.cpp
.It Fl Fl host Ar ADDR
Hostname or IP address to bind to. Default is 127.0.0.1.
.It Fl Fl port Ar PORT
Port number. Default is 8080.
.It Fl l Ar LANG , Fl Fl language Ar LANG
Default spoken language. Use 'auto' for auto-detect.
.It Fl tr , Fl Fl translate
Translate audio into English text.
.It Fl t Ar N , Fl Fl threads Ar N
Number of threads to use during computation.
.It Fl ng , Fl Fl no-gpu
Disable GPU acceleration.
.It Fl Fl gpu Ar VALUE
Select GPU backend. Values: auto, apple, amd, nvidia, disable.
.It Fl Fl log-disable
Suppress logging output.
.El
.Pp
Additional transcription options are available. Run
.Nm Fl Fl help
for the complete list.
.Sh HTTP API
.Ss GET /health
Returns server health status as JSON. Returns HTTP 503 if the model
is still loading.
.Ss POST /inference
Transcribe an audio file. Send as multipart/form-data with the audio
file in a field named "file".
.Pp
Optional form fields: response_format (json, text, srt, vtt, verbose_json),
language, translate, temperature, prompt.
.Pp
Example:
.Bd -literal -offset indent
curl http://localhost:8080/inference \\
  -F "file=@audio.wav" \\
  -F "response_format=json"
.Ed
.Ss POST /load
Load a different model at runtime.
.Bd -literal -offset indent
curl http://localhost:8080/load \\
  -F "model=/path/to/model.bin"
.Ed
.Sh DOCUMENTATION
Read our Markdown documentation for additional help and tutorials. See
the docs/whisperfile/ directory in the llamafile source repository on GitHub.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr whisperfile 1 ,
.Xr llamafile 1 ,
.Xr curl 1
